text:
Ohio Inmate Dies in Transport to Lucasville Just now share 
The Ohio State Highway Patrol is investigating the death of an inmate on a prison transport from Wednesday. 
The death has been confirmed but the identity of the deceased and the cause of death are yet to be made public. 
The death is reported to have occurred while the inmate was being transported on a bus traveling from Columbus to Lusasville. 
We will provide additional information as it is made available. iHeartCountry #TrendingTracks
